* To create VM from vagrant box
>vagrant box add ngr/trusty32-rails4.1
* To install Docker on Debian use this instructions:
https://docs.docker.com/engine/installation/linux/docker-ce/debian/


$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install  linux-image-extra-virtual
$ sudo apt-get install docker
$ sudo nano /etc/apt/sources.list

deb [arch=amd64] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu precise stable
